<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>   
<body>
    <!-- Top Nav Bar -->
<!-- Top Nav Bar -->
<%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>   

    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <main id="what-we-do">
        <!-- Introduction Section -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>At Rwanda Blood Bridge, we aim to facilitate blood donation and support hospitals with a safe, reliable blood supply. Our mission is to save lives by connecting donors and patients across Rwanda.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Programs and Services Section -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Programs and Services</h2>
            <div class="content-container">
                <img src="path/to/services.jpg" alt="Our Services" class="related-image">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p>We organize blood donation drives, offer community outreach programs, and provide support for hospitals. Our biomedical services ensure that donated blood is handled safely and efficiently.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Community Engagement Section -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Community Engagement</h2>
            <div class="content-container">
                <img src="path/to/community-engagement.jpg" alt="Community Engagement" class="related-image">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p>We believe in engaging the community through awareness programs, encouraging people to donate blood regularly, and creating a network of volunteers and partners to support our cause.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Impact Section -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Our Impact</h2>
            <p>Through our efforts, we have helped countless patients in need of blood transfusions. The impact of our work is seen in the lives saved and the growing number of regular blood donors across Rwanda.</p>
        </section>
    </main>


    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>   


</body>
</html>